            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Victoriae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Antoninianae <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Marcius <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> filius <lb n="8"/>Sextianus <lb n="9"/>Epheso <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublica</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> dedicante <lb n="2"/>Egnatio <lb n="3"/>Victore <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>et <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audio</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Pisone <lb n="8"/>legato <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>V Idus <lb n="11"/>Iunias <lb n="12"/>Apro et <lb n="13"/>Maximo <lb n="14"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil einer Basis oder Statuenbasis. Die Inschriften verteilen sich auf die Vorder- (a) und die rechte Nebenseite (b). Inschrift a: Z. 5 mit kleineren Buchstaben eingefügt. (B): Inschrift a: CIL 03, 11082: Z. 5: Antoniniana; Inschrift b: CIL 03, 04364: Z. 8/9: Zeilenfall fehlt.</p>
